# ruah demo recording

Output "./demo.gif"

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 880
Set Height 950
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "export PATH=/tmp/ruah-bin:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "export RUAH_NO_UPDATE_CHECK=1"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "npx @levi-tc/ruah demo"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
